# Coral

## Design docs (required for UI work)

**Before** implementing or changing UI, layouts, or shared components:

1. Read [`docs/design-system-2026.md`](docs/design-system-2026.md) — **complete design system for Gen Z/Millennial parents**.
2. Read [`docs/ui-design.md`](docs/ui-design.md) — shared components (`Select`, tokens, patterns).
3. Read the feature design doc when one exists (e.g. [`docs/shopping-ui-design.md`](docs/shopping-ui-design.md)).

**After** UI changes in the same session:

1. Update the relevant design doc(s) so they match the code.
2. Prefer shared components in `src/components/` — do not add one-off styled `<select>` elements.

### Design doc index

| Doc | Scope |
|-----|--------|
| `docs/design-system-2026.md` | **Master design system** — audience, colors, typography, components, motion, brand voice |
| `docs/ui-design.md` | Select, tokens, shared form/layout patterns |
| `docs/shopping-ui-design.md` | Shopping checklist, cards, grid, images |
| `docs/travel-ui-design.md` | Travel page, type tabs, tip cards |
| `docs/mom-care-ui-design.md` | Mom Care page, self-care tabs, tip cards |
| `docs/month-detail-ui-design.md` | DIY & Care grids, detail modal on month page |
| `docs/community-feature-plan.md` | **Community feature** — phased plan, memories, recipes, tips, social |

## UI components

- **Select:** `src/components/Select.jsx` — use for all dropdowns; spec in `docs/ui-design.md`.
- **Footer:** `src/components/Footer.jsx` — global footer; do not duplicate per page.

## Data and assistant (other areas)

- Assistant: see `.cursor/rules/claude.mdc` and `memory.md`.
- After data changes: `npm run verify:data` / `npm test` as appropriate.
